
    <title>Additional Health Resources</title>
    

    <%- include('../partials/header') %>

    <main class="container my-5 main-content">
        <h1 class="text-center mb-4">Additional Health Resources</h1>
        <p class="lead text-center">Take advantage of these valuable resources that will support you on your journey to better health. From apps to videos, we've got you covered.</p>

        <section>
            <h2>Health Apps</h2>
            <ul>
                <li><strong><a href="https://www.myfitnesspal.com/">MyFitnessPal</a></strong>: A calorie-tracking and fitness app that helps users set health goals, monitor nutrition, and track workouts.
                </li>
                <li><strong><a href="https://www.headspace.com/">Headspace</a></strong>: A mindfulness and meditation app that supports mental well-being through guided meditation, stress management, and sleep techniques.</li>
                <li><strong><a href="https://www.strava.com/">Strava</a></strong>: A fitness tracker for runners and cyclists to log workouts and challenge friends.</li>
            </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2>Community Support</h2>
            <ul>
                <li><strong><a href="https://www.7cups.com/">7 Cups</a></strong>: A free online emotional support community where trained listeners and therapists provide support for stress, anxiety, and mental health challenges.
                </li>
                <li><strong><a href="https://www.patientslikeme.com/">PatientsLikeMe</a>
                </strong>: A health-based social network where individuals with similar medical conditions share experiences and offer peer support.</li>
                <li><strong><a href="https://www.mentalhealth.gov/get-help/online-mental-health-services">Online Support Groups</a></strong>: Find virtual support groups for various health conditions like diabetes, mental health, and weight loss.</li>
                <li><strong><a href="https://www.verywellfit.com/find-a-support-group-4176340">Local Health Programs</a></strong>: Check for local wellness programs and support organizations in your area.</li>
            </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2>Videos</h2>
            <ul>
                <li><strong><a href="https://www.youtube.com/user/mayoclinic">Mayo Clinic YouTube Channel</a></strong>:Educational health videos covering medical conditions, treatments, and wellness tips from top healthcare professionals.
                </li>
                <li><strong><a href="https://youtube.com/@ted?si=WyKeQAKxntv9RUV9">TED Talks</a></strong>:A collection of expert-led talks on topics like mental health, fitness, nutrition, and medical breakthroughs.
                </li>
                <li><strong><a href="https://youtu.be/EvMTrP8eRvM?si=cSuNFL0pkvm_KWFe">Yoga for Beginners</a></strong>: A beginner-friendly yoga routine to get you started on your wellness journey.</li>
                <li><strong><a href="https://youtu.be/AYXfaVD5o40?si=qTYlWSHQ3QnJHWk9">Healthy Cooking</a></strong>: Videos on how to cook nutritious and delicious meals.</li>
                <li><strong><a href="https://youtu.be/rkZl2gsLUp4?si=lfiqTRAcQRVyld8k">Mental Health Talks</a></strong>: Educational videos from mental health professionals discussing stress, anxiety, and coping strategies.</li>
            </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2>Telemedicine Services</h2>
            <ul>
                <li><strong><a href="https://www.getmaple.ca/">Maple (Canada-Specific)</a></strong>: A Canadian telemedicine service that connects patients with doctors online for virtual consultations, prescriptions, and medical advice.</li>
                <li><strong><a href="https://www.teladochealth.com/">Book a Virtual Doctor Appointment</a></strong>: Links to platforms where you can schedule consultations with doctors online.</li>
                <li><strong><a href="https://www.betterhelp.com/">Mental Health Counseling</a></strong>: Online therapy platforms where you can speak with licensed therapists remotely.</li>
            </ul>
        </section>
    </main>

